OL,3,CSailor makes land after mast snaps in
OL,4,CSouthern Ocean in round-the-world race
OL,6,FA sailor from Poole has finally
OL,7,Freached land almost two weeks after a
OL,8,Fsnapped mast ended her aim to be the
OL,9,Ffirst woman to finish a 24,300 mile
OL,10,F(39,100km) race around the world for a
OL,11,Fsecond time.
OL,13,FPip Hare, 50, came 19th in the last
OL,14,Fedition of the Vendee Globe race in
OL,15,F2020. She completed the voyage in 95
OL,16,Fdays in the event's second oldest boat
OL,17,Fand becoming only the eighth woman to
OL,18,Ffinish.
