OL,3,CSailor makes land after mast snaps in
OL,4,CSouthern Ocean in round-the-world race
OL,6,FThis time, she suffered a dismast
OL,7,Fabout 800 nautical miles (1,480km)
OL,8,Fsouth of Australia in her 60ft (18m)
OL,9,Fyacht Medallia on 15 December.
OL,11,FAlmost two months into the gruelling
OL,12,Frace, she patched together a "jury
OL,13,Frig", essentially what was left of the
OL,14,Fmast and set sail to reach Melbourne,
OL,15,FAustralia, on 28 December.
OL,17,FPip said she was "bitterly
OL,18,Fdisappointed" that her race ended this
OL,19,Fway.
