OL,3,CSailor makes land after mast snaps in
OL,4,CSouthern Ocean in round-the-world race
OL,6,F"I'm also grateful that I'm in one
OL,7,Fpiece and was able to make my own way
OL,8,Fto safety," said Pip.
OL,10,FShe said: "I might be out of the race,
OL,11,Fbut the grit and determination I need
OL,12,Fto compete also helped me cope with
OL,13,Fwhat could have been a catastrophic
OL,14,Fsituation."
OL,16,FShe set up her racing team in 2019
OL,17,Fwith a #25,000 bank loan and a
OL,18,Fcrowdfunding appeal and was tipped as
OL,19,Fa top-10 finisher in the prestigious
OL,20,Fand gruelling race.
