OL,3,CSailor makes land after mast snaps in
OL,4,CSouthern Ocean in round-the-world race
OL,6,F"For me, this is my version of a World
OL,7,FCup or the Olympics," Hare said,
OL,8,Fbefore setting off. "It's the Vendee
OL,9,FGlobe race, it's the toughest sailing
OL,10,Frace in the world."
OL,12,FThe single-handed yacht race began off
OL,13,Fthe coast of France in November, and
OL,14,FPip had been in 15th place when the
OL,15,Fmast snapped.
