OL,6,FWhen asked about what it was like
OL,7,Fafter the mast broke, "in a funny way,
OL,8,FI enjoyed the slower pace of the
OL,9,Fvoyage to Australia ` ultimately, I'm
OL,10,Fa professional sailor because I love
OL,11,Fbeing out in the ocean and that's
OL,12,Fwhere I've been.
OL,14,F"Just not quite the way I expected."
OL,16,FShe said: "It didn't feel like it at
OL,17,Fthe time, but I was lucky.
