OL,6,F"When something like that happens, it
OL,7,Fcan damage the boat or I could have
OL,8,Fbeen hurt. But it happened in the
OL,9,Fdaylight, and I was able to clear up
OL,10,Fthe mess, rig a makeshift sail and
OL,11,Flimp to the nearest port."
